title: The Kissing Place (1991)
description:
Nice little thriller movie about a boy abducted at the age of 2 1/2 years old and the happy return to his lawful mother after a big adventure cross country thanks to memory recollections (at 12) when he was abducted, a must see, nice addition to your collection, this is one of my faves, notice that this is a TV show transfer, not a DVD rip, simply cause is not available in any format, if you do find a better copy please upload for us, the video is good and sound is good, WMP does play it best, DIVX player is not a good choice, but a decent one. please enjoy and seed while at it :)

Click the IMDB link for more info on this cute movie with a fantastic cast, like Meredith Baxter (kidnapper) and cute Nathaniel Moreau (Billy)
